---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import me from "../assets/me.jpeg";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
	<article class="pt-2 sm:pt-10">
		<section class="py-6">
			<div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 md:gap-4">
				<Image
					src={me}
					width={me.width}
					height={me.height}
					alt="Nicolò D'Addabbo"
					class="rounded-full my-4 w-20 h-20"
					loading="eager"
				/>
				<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
					Nicolò D&apos;Addabbo
				</h1>
			</div>
			<p class="mt-4 font-light">Software Engineer. Berlin-based.</p>
			<p class="mt-4">
				Currently working on Applied AI at <a
					class="link text-lg font-semibold"
					href="https://tesla.com"
					target="_blank">Tesla</a
				>, across software engineering, data engineering, design, and AI agents.
				End to end on everything, from business and design to development.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-4 font-light">
				I studied Computer Science and Engineering between <a
					class="link"
					target="_blank"
					href="https://polimi.it">Milan</a
				>, <a class="link" target="_blank" href="https://www.upc.edu"
					>Barcelona</a
				>, and <a
					class="link"
					target="_blank"
					href="https://www.unibo.it">Bologna</a
				>. I started building things right after high school by going
				door to door in my hometown, <a
					class="link"
					target="_blank"
					href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rimini">Rimini</a
				>, asking local businesses if they needed a website. A few said
				yes. That led to better gigs, and eventually to more complex
				mobile apps and internal tools. Along the way, I&apos;ve developed a strong interest in building
				software that&apos;s genuinely useful to people.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-4 font-light">
				I&apos;ve been a musician, Ultimate Frisbee player, and event
				organizer.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-5">
				<a
					href="https://github.com/nicolodaddabbo/"
					target="_blank"
					class="text-foreground/50 hover:text-accent transition-colors"
					aria-label="GitHub"
				>
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
						<path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/>
					</svg>
				</a>
				<a
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolodaddabbo/"
					target="_blank"
					class="text-foreground/50 hover:text-accent transition-colors"
					aria-label="LinkedIn"
				>
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
						<path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
					</svg>
				</a>
				<a
					href="mailto:nicolodaddabbo@gmail.com"
					class="text-foreground/50 hover:text-accent transition-colors"
					aria-label="Email"
				>
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
					</svg>
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="py-6">
			<h2 class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase opacity-50">Projects</h2>
			<ul class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-y-6">
				<li>
					<a class="link inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-medium" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/vistal-dev/vistal">
						Vistal
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.22 11.78a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 5.5H5.75a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5h5.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v5.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V6.56l-5.22 5.22a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
					</a>
					<p class="mt-1 font-light text-sm">Authorization layer for AI agents. Row-level security, field-level permissions, and per-user access control so LLMs can query databases without prompt-injection vulnerabilities.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a class="link inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-medium" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/nudge-libs/nudge">
						Nudge
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.22 11.78a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 5.5H5.75a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5h5.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v5.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V6.56l-5.22 5.22a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
					</a>
					<p class="mt-1 font-light text-sm">TypeScript library with a generative CLI for building prompts in code.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a class="link inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-medium" target="_blank" href="https://schedule.paganello.com">
						Paganello Schedule
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.22 11.78a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 5.5H5.75a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5h5.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v5.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V6.56l-5.22 5.22a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
					</a>
					<p class="mt-1 font-light text-sm">Real-time match schedules for Paganello, the world&apos;s largest Beach Ultimate Frisbee tournament. Over 3,000 players and attendees rely on it.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a class="link inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-medium" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/nicolodaddabbo/hykee-ai">
						HYKEE AI
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.22 11.78a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 5.5H5.75a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5h5.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v5.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V6.56l-5.22 5.22a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
					</a>
					<p class="mt-1 font-light text-sm">Virtual assistant for financial analysts interpreting Italian company balance sheets, with fine-tuned language models and in-context learning.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a class="link inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-medium" target="_blank" href="https://amslaurea.unibo.it/id/eprint/33714/">
						LLMs for Financial Statement Analysis
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.22 11.78a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 5.5H5.75a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5h5.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v5.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V6.56l-5.22 5.22a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
					</a>
					<p class="mt-1 font-light text-sm">Thesis (in Italian). Comparative study of open-source and proprietary LLMs on financial data, evaluated with expert-labeled data and a fine-tuned LLM-as-a-Judge model.</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
